  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Dental plaque is a well known etiologic factor for gingivitis. Recently, herbal extracts are
      a matter of scientific interest to inhibit plaque accumulation on teeth. The purpose of this
      study was to evaluate the effects of pistacia Mutica (PM) mouth wash on de novo dental plaque
      plaque formation, gingival inflammation indices and oral microorganisms.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
